Class NoRuleActivationsHardObjective

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.BaseObjective
      • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.NoRuleActivationsHardObjective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObjective

    public class NoRuleActivationsHardObjective
extends BaseObjective
    This hard objective is satisfied if there are no rule activations from the current state (returning 1 in this case).
    Author:
    Andras Szabolcs Nagy
